org.openimaj.util.parallel.partition

Class FixedSizeChunkPartitioner<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.util.parallel.partition.FixedSizeChunkPartitioner<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of object in the partition
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Partitioner<T>

    public class FixedSizeChunkPartitioner<T>
extends Object
implements Partitioner<T>
    A FixedSizeChunkPartitioner dynamically partitions data into chunks of a fixed length. The partitioner does not need to know about the length of the data apriori.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
